\b\fs28 \cf0 What if\'85?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl360\slmult1\sa240\partightenfactor0

\b0\fs24 \cf0 So, let\'92s imagine an institution like the State Archives of Belgium, with million of data collected for years, wishes to make them more visible and shareable by publishing them in the LOD cloud. \
However, as seen in the previous slide, some properties are currently missing to express some concepts.\
There would be 2 main options for improvement in this case:\
